graph TB
    subgraph "KServe Component"
        Controller[kserve-controller-manager<br/>Go Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        StorageInit[storage-initializer<br/>Python Init Container]
        Agent[agent<br/>Go Sidecar]
        Router[router<br/>Go Service]
        ModelServers[model-servers<br/>MLServer/TorchServe/Triton]
        LocalController[localmodel-controller<br/>Go Controller]
        LocalAgent[localmodel-node-agent<br/>Go DaemonSet]

        Controller -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
        Controller -->|creates| ModelServers
        Controller -->|injects| StorageInit
        Controller -->|injects| Agent
        Agent -->|proxies requests| ModelServers
        StorageInit -->|loads models| ModelServers
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService<br/>v1beta1]
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime<br/>v1alpha1]
        TrainedModelCR[TrainedModel<br/>v1alpha1]
        InferenceGraphCR[InferenceGraph<br/>v1alpha1]
        LLMCR[LLMInferenceService<br/>v1alpha1]
        LocalModelCacheCR[LocalModelCache<br/>v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Knative[Knative Serving<br/>v1.x]
        Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>1.x]
        KEDA[KEDA<br/>v2.x]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>v1.x]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        ODHOperator[OpenDataHub Operator]
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    end

    subgraph "External Services"
        S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        GCS[Google Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Azure[Azure Blob<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR
    User -->|creates| LLMCR

    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|referenced by| Controller
    TrainedModelCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceGraphCR -->|watched by| Controller
    LLMCR -->|watched by| Controller
    LocalModelCacheCR -->|watched by| LocalController

    Controller -->|creates| Knative
    Controller -->|creates| Istio
    Controller -->|creates| KEDA
    Webhook -->|cert from| CertManager

    ODHOperator -->|enables/disables| Controller
    Dashboard -->|manages| InferenceServiceCR
    Controller -.->|references| ModelRegistry

    StorageInit -->|downloads models| S3
    StorageInit -->|downloads models| GCS
    StorageInit -->|downloads models| Azure

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style StorageInit fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
